	<trait>
		<name>Personality Trait</name>
		<text>Choose or randomly determine</text>
		<text></text>
		<text>1. I'm haunted by fey laughter that only I can hear, though I know it's just my mind playing tricks on me. </text>
		<text> </text>
		<text>2. Like a nomad, I can't settle down in one place for very long. </text>
		<text> </text>
